"     Sara Ellis Simonsen, CNM, MSPH, PhD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?17/9/17556/contributors\">",
"     Michael W Varner, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
