"     </div>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <div class=\"reference\">",
"      Gelperin K, \"Psychiatric Adverse Events With Drug Treatments of ADHD,\" available at: file://www.fda.gov/ohrms/dockets/ac/06/slides/2006-4210s-index.htm. Accessed May 25, 2006.",
"     </div>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
